==Published works==
*''Just the Way I Am: Poetic Selections on Reasons to Live, Reasons to Love and Reasons to Smile from the Songs of Dolly Parton'' (1979)<ref>{{cite book|title=Just the Way I Am: Poetic Selections on "Reasons to Live, Reasons to Love and Reasons to Smile" from the Songs of Dolly Parton|publisher=Blue Mountain Press|language=English|date=1979|isbn=978-0883960431}}</ref>
